    "description": "Grow your career with Axis Bank! We are hiring a Risk Analyst for our Madurai team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Axis Bank:\nAxis Bank is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Axis Bank!",
